  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0ba9\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 21\u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel for registered vehicles from 21st",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kumara Rajapaksh, president of Fuel Station Owners Association, said that the operation of fuel distribution to vehicles registered for fuel will start next Thursday.",
        "He said this while referring to the date on which the operation of fuel distribution to vehicles registered on the website will start.",
        "Due to the National Fuel Permit, fuel supply will start from next Thursday. So there is no point in queuing in front of Sibetco filling stations. Kyiv from Thursday. R. Fuel will be dispensed only based on code and vehicle registration number.",
        "So people currently queuing in front of fuel stations should move away from that place.",
        "Accordingly, only vehicle owners whose last digit of the vehicle registration number is 0, 1 and 2 should come to get fuel on the 21st."
      ],
